&lt;p&gt;अतः सही उत्तर &lt;strong&gt;विकल्प (4)&lt;/strong&gt; है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;According to the given information;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Only two people sit to the right of C-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/12/F3_Madhuri_Defence_16.12.2022_D49.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 272px; height: 67px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Only two people sit between B and C-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
