&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/12/F3_Madhuri_Defence_16.12.2022_D51.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 272px; height: 67px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;E is an immediate neighbour of A and B-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
